<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r2" locked="0" aEditID="c1r2" >
<![CDATA[<table height="400" width="600" cellpadding="5" border="0" cellspacing="5"><tbody><tr height="300" valign="top"><td teditid="c1r2" aeditid="c1r2" locked="0" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-31f038fb-4ffa-e3cc-c8f8-e5f52f048f46"><font size="2"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact__c},</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-aff5d6ba-3391-7ac8-93ba-2c6a803a30ca"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Payment schedule for {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}, clause 4.1</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Payment information for your employment contract with us on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} is listed below. This information is subject to you completing your employment with us in conjunction with the conditions in your contract.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38;">Payment Overview</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You have been allocated to </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">as a <b>Residential Mentor</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Wave Contract dates are {!Job_placement__c.Assignment_start_date__c} and {!Job_placement__c.Assignment_end_date__c} ("Work Period") plus {!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} days ("</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Holiday Period</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">"); together referred to as a Wave Contract (a "</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Wave Contrac</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">t"). </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You will be paid an amount of £375. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The amounts are calculated on the basis that you will work all days required of your role; any days or half days that you are absent or no longer required to work will be deducted from your pay.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">All of your pay will be subject to tax and National Insurance (NI) deductions. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You will be able to review tax deductions on your payslip which is sent to you via email two days prior to your payment date.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><font face="Arial"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">N.B </span></font><span style="font-size: 12.8000001907349px; font-family: Arial; line-height: 17.9400005340576px; white-space: pre-wrap;">All Residential Mentors are required to work an additional day before the first wave and after their last wave <b><i>depending</i></b> on their geographical area (this will be paid at the daily rate)</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">​.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;"><br></span></p></font><font size="2"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38;">When will I receive this payment?</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You will be paid for your role on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} on </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}</span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We pay our seasonal staff on a monthly basis. We aim to pay seasonal staff within 5 weeks of their completing a wave (where possible). For an overview of our payment dates and the corresponding waves, please see </span><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Summer2015PaymentTimetable_(1)_1.pdf" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">this document</span></a><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">What next?</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You will receive a ‘Payment Notification’ email outlining your approved pay at the end of each wave. Please note that if you are working multiple waves over the summer, you will receive a new payment notification email for each work period.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Workplace pension auto-enrollment: </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Due to new auto-enrollment legislation, employees of The Challenge, including a small number of seasonal staff, will be enrolled into a workplace pension scheme. Auto-enrollment does not occur until October 2015 and staff will have the opportunity to opt-out at this point. To see if you qualify for auto-enrollment, please see our </span><span style="font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Any questions? </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">If you have any queries about the payment schedule please </span><span style="font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/contact/">contact your local staffing team</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">, quoting the email reference number below in any correspondence. Alternatively, you can look through our ‘Payment, Advances and Expenses’ </span><span style="font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.15;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Best wishes,</span></p></font></span></div></td></tr><tr height="50" valign="top"><td teditid="c1r3" aeditid="c1r3" locked="0" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: small; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Challenge</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: small; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">NCS Programme</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: small; line-height: 1.38;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: small; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Email reference: CA 9.6c</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>]]></td>
